            <title>[CXF-6842] Unwrap exception nested with WebApplicationException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-6842</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In a resource class, if an exception is thrown which is nested with WebApplicationException, cxf can try to get the cause and create response from WebApplicationException&lt;/p&gt;</description>
